Class ModelEquipment

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.ModelEquipment

  • public class ModelEquipment
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for storing data retrieved from the queries in database.DbEquipmentList The getters on the koie names is only used for filling in the table in KoieEksempel
